      *-------------------------------------------------------------
     C           #UPSC     BEGSR
      *
     C                     Z-ADD*ZERO     WRRN    40
     C           *IN90     DOUEQ*ON
     C                     ADD  1         WRRN
     C           WRRN      CHAINSFL02                90
     C           *IN90     IFEQ *OFF
     C           S@UPID    ANDNE*BLANK
     C           S@SERL    CHAINAC#PL71              95
     C           *IN95     IFEQ *OFF
      * DO NOT CAHNGE DATE AND TIME TO KEEP CREATE DATE AND TIME
 JW  C**                   Z-ADD*YEAR     EKKOYY
  .  C**                   Z-ADD*MONTH    EKKOMM
  .  C**                   Z-ADD*DAY      EKKODD
 JW  C**                   TIME           EKTIME
      * SCAN DATE AND TIME
     C                     MOVEL#USER     EKKOME
     C                     Z-ADD*YEAR     EKDEYY
     C                     Z-ADD*MONTH    EKDEMM
     C                     Z-ADD*DAY      EKDEDD
     C                     TIME           EKDETM
      *
     C                     Z-ADDS@QTY     EKSRYO
     C                     UPDATAC#PP701
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
